Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:04.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见  美伟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:07.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:09.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:11.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:14.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么毫无联络啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:19.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还以为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:32.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:36.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法学姐跟黑妻认识？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:16.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然没有明说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:18.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要说这个黑妻…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大蜘蛛的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18\fsp-1}Big Spider
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:26.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个黑妻跟固法学姐为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟像这种会随便袭击女孩子的家伙认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊  不是那个黑妻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说黑子  你也帮忙说明一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有缘分是要慢慢品尝的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:49.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事情请允许我静观其变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  很在意啊  真让人心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  干脆直接去问固法学姐试试！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:01.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈在这几天都没在支部里出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:09.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前的能力者袭击事件还没解决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说问题就出在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里也做不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:17.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候还是移步到别处比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移步到别处…要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:33.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这里是固法美伟学姐的房间…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是美伟的后辈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  现在她刚好出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:44.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  还想打听黑妻的事情的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们改日再来  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的拿她没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连后辈们都得担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑妻回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到他还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您认识黑妻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…学姐跟黑妻是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…先等一下  在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把你们那边的情况说给我听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:31.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那么为什么固法学姐会认识黑妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  学姐之前抓住过黑妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美伟她啊  以前是大蜘蛛的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(365,328)\fs18\fsp-1}Big Spider
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能  无论如何这也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  学姐可是风纪委员啊  怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看她这样  她以前可是个不良呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是不良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:59.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不喜欢评论他人的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么说固法学姐是强能力能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Level 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去的地方应该还有很多才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:10.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么偏偏参加作为无能力者集团的武装无能力集团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:10.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,328)\fs18\fsp3}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没遇到过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力遇到瓶颈的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:19.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还很难突破而因此灰心的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的美伟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给人感觉就像去哪都没有归宿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与闪耀着光芒的人们相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然称之为武装无能力集团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18\fsp3}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:07.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也就是跟些趣味相投的伙伴们一起做傻事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  当初我也很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:16.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用得着故意把自己是能力者的事隐瞒起来去呆在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:17.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:25.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大蜘蛛是我能够展现自我的地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:25.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(209,328)\fs18\fsp-1}Big Spider
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美伟曾经这样说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独感…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:37.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找自我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦身在学园都市总会沾上的麻疹一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那时的美伟也沾上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人一辈子只会染上一次麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（美伟与黑）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:15.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你…是异能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:15.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就别在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:17.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的归宿只有这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力者还真够麻烦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:35.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年后年  你还打算留在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  做决定的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然固法学姐是武装无能力集团让我倍受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(331,328)\fs18\fsp3}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此为什么要抛开风纪委员的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么联系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:16.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去是过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的学姐不是在风纪委员里努力工作了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:24.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们很温柔  偶尔会变得很严厉  还很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜欢这样的学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么事到如今还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能那么简单地分开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且正因为有过去的自己才会有现在的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:40.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  倘若这过去还很特别的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:41.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂不更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是反对御坂学姐的看法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  果然还是弄不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:00.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  来的人真少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法吧  那种事情刚过不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:09.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  黑妻大哥…是假的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑妻大哥就是黑妻大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当那个人叫他蛇谷的时候好像被吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:18.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…被吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁…害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑妻大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有空怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:33.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不马上给我去把那个假货找出来宰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园都市里不需要两个黑妻绵流！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:39.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…赶快找！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:40.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:41.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？能力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18\fsp-1.5}Capacity Down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:07.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里也乱成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是袭击能力者的时…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐从那开始就一直这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？警备员发邮件来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备员总部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会对武装无能力集团所进行的袭击能力者事件展开反击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,328)\fs18\fsp3}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:38.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天早晨将一同对第十学区G区域通称Strange进行全面镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.78,spec2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,110)}警备员总部将会对武装无能力集团\N所进行的袭击能力者事件展开反击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.78,spec2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,89)\fs8}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.78,spec2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(159,89)\fs8\fsp3}Skill Out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.78,spec2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,150)}从明天早晨将一同对第十学区G区域\N通称Strange进行全面镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.78,spec2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,189)}作为支援请风纪委员出动进行情报收集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.78,spec2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,178)\fs8}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:49.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美伟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:19.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去把明天全面镇压的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉黑妻么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这里不是固法学姐该待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:30.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是我该待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:34.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这个事实告诉我的正是黑妻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长别去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.62,spec4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,100)\frz-6}蛇谷这个笨蛋在我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.62,spec4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(388,122)\frz-6}想要回去就一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  总不能抛弃蛇谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个明显是陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  接着上次的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:59.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得这里不是你该留下名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:18.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我赶到的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  才有了现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就算是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐不是风纪委员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却想要将犯人放走  这太不合常理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不合常理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以来已经两年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后  当我睁开眼睛时  已经身处医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后被转移到设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:07.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正出来  其实也就是半年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:16.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还以为自己再也没有机会眺望这番风景了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾觉得  还是不要再见你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦相见  又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又打算独自一人承受一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:25.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蜘蛛是我一手创立的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18\fsp-1}Big Spider
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:31.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要由我亲手将它捣毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:33.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是警备员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:33.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自替别人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心所欲地行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:44.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你这样  我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才会来到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:53.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你也差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  她从刚才起就一副为难的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜现在自己身边的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再留下那样的回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧  美伟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今已经时过境迁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也好  过去也罢  这又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算容身之处改变了  我的心意是始终如一的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算时光流逝  所处的立场发生改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却仍然坚定不移的感情真的存在么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:46.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说  一个人对别人的感情就该是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  通过那份感情的不断累积
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使那个人的现在熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积累…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样想有点一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实姐姐大人和我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然相处时间并不算长久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却也积累了一份深厚的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:12.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今后也将继续积累下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个小请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:36.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在将要进行的是针对第十学区G区域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通称「Strange」地区的全面镇压行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:40.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:54.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  这是干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然少不了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就一副忙碌的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来做个了结的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  是上次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你也该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很强的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你的确很强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那样的话能力者也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能胜过数量和武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美伟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺帅气的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固法大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:17.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变成了相当下贱的男人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仗势欺人  还手持武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:23.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了我们跑去当风纪委员的你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:30.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们见识见识我们的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次直接送进你们的身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们还有那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:49.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:55.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会在指望我们在同一个坑里摔两次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动手  干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可是常盘台的超电磁炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超电磁炮？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就把你们给干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也让学姐我出出风头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:23.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全力冲过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全提不起干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个电击棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:54.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就算赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:30.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是哪个时代的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们再向前试试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心把你们全炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:43.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  吓得不敢动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要点火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:57.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的那段时光可真是愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来  我让你别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家围在一块儿  尽干些傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过…来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:22.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:24.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能容下我们的地方只有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要集结大蜘蛛的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18\fsp-1}Big Spider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就必须化身为黑妻才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:36.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你的存在是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:53.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容身之处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:57.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指能够展现自我的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成  大功告成～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美伟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:21.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑妻绵流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:25.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以涉嫌暴力伤害的罪名逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺适合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件皮夹克  你的胸口不觉得紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:43.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  每天都有喝那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:49.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然牛奶还是武藏野的好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话题果然转到胸部了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不令人反感…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:21:59.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:03.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:04.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的风的确很舒适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:05.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:08.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了这个特意跑来这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:12.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这年头居然还有人画姻缘伞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:14.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美？  小黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:18.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:22.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会有一个人对另一个人的心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:29.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园都市么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记学长的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:35.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所教导我的各种各样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉升天一般的身为女人的愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这糟糕的台词是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:40.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚游戏啦


